	* src/core/misc.c: parse_time_interval: x days were actually
	returned as hours. weeks were returned as hours*7.. which also
	means I calculated the max. return value of over 1 year wrong. It's
	actually 24 days, but it's hopefully enough. Removed "weeks" unit
	to discourage usage of large values..

